high_descs: Turn around and walk halfway to the door, then turn right and walk to the fridge, then turn right and walk to the sink and face it.
Take the apple from the sink.
Turn around and look up at the microwave above the stove.
Heat the apple in the microwave then take it out.
Turn around and face the sink.
Put the apple in the sink.
anns.task_desc: Use the microwave to heat an apple.

high_descs: Turn around and move towards the door next to the shelves. Turn right and move towards the refrigerator and turn right once past the black rubbish bin. Move to the sink and turn right to face the sink.
Pick up the green apple in the corner of the sink to the right of the mug.
Turn left and move to the oven and then turn left to face the microwave above the oven.
Place the green apple on the plate in the microwave, microwave the green apple, then open the microwave and pick up the green apple.
Turn left and move to the sink in the kitchen island.
Place the green apple in the sink between the two onions in front of the drain.
anns.task_desc: Place a heated apple in the sink.

high_descs: Turn around and go towards the door, take a right and go towards the fridge, take a right and go to the sink on your right.
Pick up the green apple that is in the sink.
Turn around and go to the microwave that is above the stove.
Open the microwave, put the apple inside, close the door, turn the microwave on to cook, remove the apple from the microwave and close the door.
Turn around and go back to the sink.
Put the apple in the sink between the two eggs.
anns.task_desc: Put a cooked apple in a sink.

high_descs: Turn around and walk to the sink that is on your right
Pick up the green apple out of the sink
Turn around and walk to the microwave that is above the stove
Open the microwave and place the apple inside to the left of the green cup
Close the door and turn the microwave on then open the microwave and pick up the apple
Turn around and place the apple in the sink between the two eggs closest to you
anns.task_desc: Put an apple into a microwave to cook it
